---
---

<section id="perfiles" class="py-32 bg-grid relative">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-20 animate-on-scroll">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">
        Perfiles <span class="text-gradient-animated">disponibles</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Cada perfil está optimizado para un tipo de tarea específico. Elige el que mejor se adapte a tu flujo de trabajo.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="animate-on-scroll delay-1 group relative bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 card-hover glow-effect">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-violet-500/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-violet-500/20 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-violet-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Claude Universal</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">Configuración base que reduce el output verbose manteniendo la calidad. Ahorra ~63% de tokens.</p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-violet-500/10 text-violet-400 text-xs rounded-md">Cualquier proyecto</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="animate-on-scroll delay-2 group relative bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 card-hover glow-effect">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-cyan-500/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-cyan-500/20 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Claude Coding</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">Código primero, explicación después. Sin boilerplate, sin abstracciones prematuras.</p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-cyan-500/10 text-cyan-400 text-xs rounded-md">Dev projects</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-cyan-500/10 text-cyan-400 text-xs rounded-md">Debug</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="animate-on-scroll delay-3 group relative bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 card-hover glow-effect">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-500/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-emerald-500/20 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Claude Benchmark</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">Configuración mínima para tests de eficiencia. Máxima reducción de tokens.</p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400 text-xs rounded-md">Tests</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400 text-xs rounded-md">Pipelines</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="animate-on-scroll delay-4 group relative bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 card-hover glow-effect">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-500/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-amber-500/20 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-amber-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Claude Analysis</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">Output centrado en datos con reglas estrictas de precisión. Sin alucinaciones.</p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-400 text-xs rounded-md">Datos</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-400 text-xs rounded-md">Research</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="animate-on-scroll delay-5 group relative bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 card-hover glow-effect">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-rose-500/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-rose-500/20 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-rose-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Claude Agents</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">Output estructurado para automatización. JSON, bullets, tablas. Sin prosa innecesaria.</p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-rose-500/10 text-rose-400 text-xs rounded-md">Bots</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-rose-500/10 text-rose-400 text-xs rounded-md">Automatización</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="animate-on-scroll delay-5 group relative bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 card-hover glow-effect">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-blue-500/20 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 9l3 3-3 3m5 0h3M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">OpenCode & Gemini</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">Configuraciones universales para OpenCode y Gemini con las mismas reglas de eficiencia.</p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-400 text-xs rounded-md">OpenCode</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-400 text-xs rounded-md">Gemini</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
